<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ870901-0062 </DOCNO><HL> Dividend News:Independent Bank Corp.Declares 3-for-2 Stock Split</HL><DD> 09/01/87</DD><SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO><IN> INDBDIVIDENDS (DIV) </IN><DATELINE> ROCKLAND, Mass.  </DATELINE><TEXT>   Independent Bank Corp. declared a 3-for-2 stock split to holders of record Sept. 8. The bank didn't say when the shares will be distributed.    The bank also said it plans to seek shareholder approval to sell 600,000 common shares in a public offering this year. Independent Bank has about 3.3 million shares outstanding.    In national over-the-counter trading yesterday, Independent Bank closed at $21.25, up 37.5 cents. </TEXT></DOC>